column1: Supplementary Table 1. Data on individual collared flycatcher song repertoires recorded in the Pilis Mountains, Hungary. The table contains information on the year a given recording was made (year), the song recordings' ID (recID), the individuals' ring number (ring) and the universally decoded syllable type IDs (univ_syll_types) that make it available to compare repertoires within- and between-individuals. Where the ring numbers are not available, distinction between individual repertoires can be made with the help of the recordings' ID.
